function.name: str_replace_editor

extras.diff:
--- /tmp/solution.py
+++ /tmp/solution.py
@@ -0,0 +1 @@
+n, r = map(int, input().split())
@@ -1,0 +3,15 @@
+for _ in range(n):
+    d, a = map(int, input().split())
+
+    # Check if eligible for rating update based on division
+    if d == 1:
+        # Div. 1: rating between 1600 and 2799
+        if 1600 <= r <= 2799:
+            r += a
+    else:  # d == 2
+        # Div. 2: rating between 1200 and 2399
+        if 1200 <= r <= 2399:
+            r += a
+
+print(r)
+
